# Plot Output Format

Always save plots as **PNG**, never PDF.

```r
# ✅ GOOD
ggsave("my_plot.png", p, width = 9, height = 5, dpi = 150)

# ❌ BAD
ggsave("my_plot.pdf", p, width = 9, height = 5)
```

This applies to all R scripts in the repo (`scripts/`, `vignettes/`, etc.).
